18:38.285 --> 18:41.354
How are those, um,
algebra problems coming?

18:41.354 --> 18:43.390
Good, yeah.

18:43.390 --> 18:45.192
I really think they're
starting to get it.

18:45.192 --> 18:46.726
Well, good.

18:46.726 --> 18:49.362
